text: Desmiphora maculosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Linsley and Chemsak in 1966. It is known from the Galapagos Islands.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora maculosa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1966
title: Desmiphora maculosa
